==鐵路==
[[File:Mina_2012_29.JPG|250px]]
由於沙烏地阿拉伯過度依賴陸運與空運，鐵路方面的投資相對較少，不過目前正在興建的[[哈拉曼高速鐵路|哈拉曼高速鐵路計畫]]預計將於2015年底完工<ref name="railjournal.com">{{cite web |url= http://www.railjournal.com/index.php/middle-east/testing-set-to-begin-on-saudi-high-speed-line.html?channel=542 |title= Testing set to begin on Saudi High Speed Line. IRJ |accessdate= 2015-11-01 |archive-date= 2015-09-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150924121528/http://www.railjournal.com/index.php/middle-east/testing-set-to-begin-on-saudi-high-speed-line.html?channel=542 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arabnews.com/news/saudi-arabia/610201 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-11-01 |archive-date=2015-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016081511/http://www.arabnews.com/news/saudi-arabia/610201 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，將連結[[麥加|麥加]]、[[吉达|吉达]]與[[麥地那|麥地那]]等城市，理論速度可達320公里/小時<ref name="brief">{{cite news | title=Project brief | url=http://www.saudirailexpansion.com/SaudiRailExpansion/inner.aspx?parent=421&secserno=427&prosecno=421 | work=Saudi Railways Expansion Programme | access-date=2015-11-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091218204914/http://www.saudirailexpansion.com/SaudiRailExpansion/inner.aspx?parent=421&secserno=427&prosecno=421 | archive-date=2009-12-18 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>，營運速度約為300公里/小時<ref name=arwmmcc>{{cite news | title =Al Rajhi wins Makkah – Madinah civils contract | url =http://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view/10/al-rajhi-wins-makkah-madinah-civils-contract.html | work =[[Railway_Gazette_International|Railway Gazette International]] | date =2009-02-09 | accessdate =2015-11-01 | archive-date =2010-06-19 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20100619124810/http://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view/10/al-rajhi-wins-makkah-madinah-civils-contract.html | dead-url =no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.ptferroviaria.es/Portals/0/PTFE/PTFE-Documents/Mariano-Garrido.pdf |title= Proyecto Meca-Medina Asamblea de la PTFE |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120627203123/http://www.ptferroviaria.es/Portals/0/PTFE/PTFE-Documents/Mariano-Garrido.pdf |archivedate= 2012-06-27 }}</ref>。另一項[[麦加捷运|麦加捷运]]則是在麥加城市裡的一條長約18公里的輕軌，營運始於2010年<ref name=opening>{{cite journal |url=http://www.railwaygazette.com/nc/news/single-view/view/hajj-pilgrims-take-the-metro-to-makkah.html |title=Hajj pilgrims take the metro to Makkah |journal=[[Railway_Gazette_International|Railway Gazette International]] |date=November 15, 2010 |accessdate=2014-05-08 |archive-date=2010-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101203184240/http://www.railwaygazette.com/nc/news/single-view/view/hajj-pilgrims-take-the-metro-to-makkah.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2014年，沙烏地阿拉伯鐵路總長1,378公里，全都是1.435公尺[[軌距|軌距]]的標準軌，鐵路長度位居世界第81位<ref name=CIAfact/>。

==海運==
沙烏地阿拉伯擁有許多良好的港口，主要用於運輸[[石油|石油]]產品，沙烏地阿拉伯港務局負責海運這方面的業務<ref>{{cite web|author1=PORTS AUTHORITY|title=Introduction to Ports Authority|url=http://www.ports.gov.sa/english/pages/default.aspx|website=http://www.ports.gov.sa/|publisher=PORTS AUTHORITY|accessdate=2015-11-01|archive-date=2015-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151113002010/http://www.ports.gov.sa/english/Pages/default.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以下列出主要的港口：
*靠近[[波斯灣|波斯灣]]一側：[[达曼_(沙特阿拉伯)|达曼]]具有1,492,315的貨櫃量，為波斯灣測最大的港口<ref name=CIAfact/>、[[朱拜勒_(沙烏地阿拉伯)|朱拜勒 (沙烏地阿拉伯)]]、[[拉斯坦努拉|拉斯坦努拉]]、[[海夫吉|海夫吉]]、[[阿可賀巴|阿可賀巴]]
*靠近[[紅海|紅海]]一側：[[吉达|吉达]]每年有4,010,448的貨櫃量，為沙烏地阿拉伯全國最大港口<ref name=CIAfact/>、[[延布|延布]]、[[利斯|利斯]]、[[杜巴_(沙特阿拉伯)|杜巴]]、[[拉比格|拉比格]]、[[吉贊|吉贊]]、[[法拉桑群島|法拉桑群島]]

==空運==
截至2013年，沙烏地阿拉伯具有82座鋪設跑道的機場與132座未鋪設跑道的機場，共計214座機場<ref name=CIAfact/>，跑道超過3047公尺的有七座，介於2348~3047公尺之間的則有23座之多<ref name=CIAfact/>。另外有10座直昇機專屬機場<ref name=CIAfact/>。
==管路運輸==
沙烏地阿拉伯國內的管線數量相當多，管線種類也相當多元化，其中冷凝管線長達209公里；天然氣管線更有2940公里、[[液化石油氣|液化石油氣]]則有1183公里；最長的原油管線有5117公里；而提煉後的汽油成品管線有1151公里長<ref name=CIAfact/>。

